    "There are also computational uncertainties, such as the feasibility of training and updating DNNs effectively in a smartphone environment.",
    "Furthermore, these networks have to function in real-time, adding another layer of complexity to the system [142].Ensuring coordination between multiple elements, such as facial analysis and the monitoring of hand movements, is also essential for providing a comprehensive assessment.",
